species group, but is now placed in the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Dobson" authorityYear="1877" box="[3057,3235,2467,2506]" class="Mammalia" family="Hipposideridae" genus="Hipposideros" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="246" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="calcaratus">
